107
00:13:37,138 --> 00:13:39,595
Is it really possible?

108
00:13:41,843 --> 00:13:44,659
Stop insulting Mother Mary.

109
00:13:44,725 --> 00:13:48,468
She got pregnant
because she had a lover.

110
00:13:50,326 --> 00:13:52,270
