We won't study
with assistant nuns.

118
00:14:10,974 --> 00:14:14,074
- Expel them!
- Wait.

119
00:14:14,143 --> 00:14:18,653
You can't judge all of us
by Sister Ishida alone.

120
00:14:18,721 --> 00:14:21,885
We came here

121
00:14:21,954 --> 00:14:23,929
